# askEnum(property, turn)
- Which value do you want for {toLower(property)}?

# askNumber(property, turn)
- IF: {turn.schema.properties[property].minimum && turn.schema.properties[property].maximum}
- Enter a number for {toLower(property)} between {turn.schema.properties[property].minimum} and {turn.schema.properties[property].maximum}
- ELSE:
- Enter a number for {toLower(property)}

# askString(property, turn)
- Enter a value for {toLower(property)}

